ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I definitely would suggest this class to students interested in algebraic geometry.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: This class deepen my knowledge in algebraic geometry and modular forms theory, it exploited connections between the two branches and gave me a better understanding of notion familiar to experts in representation theory (Hecke operators). Also, provided the constructions of the moduli space of elliptic curves over a base scheme that I found to be very detailed.
